ice-0,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:120\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:120\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,N/A,frontend-2,hipstershop.Frontend/Recv.,13,HTTP status code: 500,出现次数:117\naiops-k8s-08,productcatalogservice,frontend-1,productcatalogservice-0,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:51\naiops-k8s-06,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:51\naiops-k8s-06,frontend,N/A,frontend-1,hipstershop.Frontend/Recv.,13,HTTP status code: 500,出现次数:49\naiops-k8s-08,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-0,checkoutservice-0,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-08,checkoutservice,frontend-2,checkoutservice-0,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"0PUK6V6EV0\"\"\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-01,productcatalogservice,checkoutservice-0,productcatalogservice-2,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"2ZYFJ3GM2N\"\"\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"0PUK6V6EV0\"\"\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,checkoutservice,frontend-2,checkoutservice-0,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"2ZYFJ3GM2N\"\"\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,productcatalogservice,checkoutservice-0,productcatalogservice-0,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:1\n", "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-28T00:10:09Z to 2025-06-28T00:24:09Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-28 00:10:09+00:00 to 2025-06-28 00:24:09+00:00"}, "log_analysis_findings": "根据收集到的日志数据，以下是分析结果：\n\n### 关键发现：\n1. **错误模式**：\n   - 多个日志条目显示 `Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`，这表明数据库或存储服务出现了区域不可用的问题。\n   - 错误主要出现在 `frontend` 和 `productcatalogservice` 服务中。\n\n2. **涉及的服务**：\n   - `frontend` 服务在尝试获取产品或推荐产品时失败。\n   - `productcatalogservice` 服务在查询产品时失败。\n\n3. **公共嫌疑人**：\n   - `productcatalogservice` 是多个服务抱怨的目标，可能是根因。\n\n### 分析结果：\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Error 9005 (HY000)\", \"Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error\", \"failed to query product\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"数据库区域不可用导致查询失败，错误代码为 Error 9005 (HY000)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 下一步建议：\n1. **检查数据库状态**：确认 `productcatalogservice` 依赖的数据库是否正常运行。\n2. **验证网络连接**：确保 `productcatalogservice` 能够正常访问数据库。\n3. **监控数据库性能**：检查是否有性能瓶颈或资源不足的问题。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的追踪数据，我已经对故障时间段2025-06-28T00:10:09Z到2025-06-28T00:24:09Z的系统故障进行了分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"productcatalogservice->tidb\", \"frontend->productcatalogservice\", \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice出现大量'Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable'错误，错误次数超过170次，涉及frontend和checkoutservice的调用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice->tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"GetProduct操作延迟异常增加：正常平均耗时约10秒，异常时段延迟高达38-39秒，延迟倍数超过3800倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend接收到大量HTTP 500错误（共166次），是productcatalogservice错误传播的直接受害者\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice在PlaceOrder操作中也出现错误，无法获取产品信息，是productcatalogservice故障的间接受害者\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 关键发现分析：\n\n**根因定位**：`productcatalogservice`是明确的故障根因，因为它：\n1. **最下游异常**：作为数据库访问层，是调用链的最下游\n2. **错误起始点**：出现\"Region is unavailable\"数据库错误\n3. **严重延迟**：响应时间从10秒激增至38-39秒\n\n**故障传播路径**：\n```\nTiDB (Region unavailable) → productcatalogservice → frontend/checkoutservice → 用户端HTTP 500错误\n```\n\n**影响范围**：\n- 主要影响：产品目录查询功能（GetProduct操作）\n- 次要影响：推荐服务和结账服务\n- 影响节点：aiops-k8s-08和aiops-k8s-06节点上的服务\n\n故障的根本原因是productcatalogservice与TiDB数据库的连接问题，导致Region unavailable错误，进而引发整个系统的级联故障。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的监控数据，我现在对故障期间的系统状态进行分析。从指标数据来看，系统在指定时间段内出现了多个关键服务异常。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"duration_99th\", \"memory_usage\", \"failed_query_ops\", \"store_unhealth_count\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio和rrt_max指标严重异常，错误率从0%飙升到60%，最大响应时间从12.5秒激增至4027万秒\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-2的error_ratio从0.0升至60.0，rrt_max从12479.5升至40276558.0，变化率均超过199%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"server_error_ratio和error_ratio指标异常，服务端错误率从0%升至26.32%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-1的server_error_ratio从0.0升至26.32，error_ratio从0.0升至26.32，p99变化率200%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"duration_99th和memory_usage指标异常，数据库响应时间从10ms激增至64.88秒，内存使用异常波动\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-tidb的duration_99th从0.01升至64.88，memory_usage从1010MB降至564MB，存在failed_query_ops异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt指标严重异常，响应时间从7.37秒激增至1689万秒\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-0的rrt从7369.92升至16891505.08，变化率199.83%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-pd\",\n      \"reason\": \"store_unhealth_count指标异常，显示存储节点健康状态异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-pd的store_unhealth_count从0.0升至1.0，表明数据库集群存在节点健康问题\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结：**\n\n1. **主要故障模式**：多个服务出现严重的性能降级和错误率飙升，特别是productcatalogservice和frontend服务\n2. **数据库影响**：TiDB数据库出现响应时间激增和存储节点健康问题，可能是底层原因\n3. **服务级联故障**：productcatalogservice的异常可能影响了依赖它的frontend服务\n4. **关键指标**：错误率、响应时间、数据库性能指标均显示严重异常\n\n建议进一步分析日志和追踪数据来确认具体的故障链和根本原因。"}
